WEBVTT

00:01.902 --> 00:03.236
<i>PREVIOUSLY ON "THE HAVES</i>
<i>AND THE HAVE NOTS"...</i>

00:03.236 --> 00:04.638
YOU EVEN TOLD MY DAD.
YOU SAID I HIT SOMEONE.

00:04.638 --> 00:05.305
YOU KNOW.

00:05.305 --> 00:06.907
TELL ME WHAT I KNOW.

00:06.907 --> 00:09.776
MY SON WYATT
IS NOT GOING TO LAST A DAY

00:09.776 --> 00:10.844
WITH YOUR ACCOMMODATIONS.

00:10.844 --> 00:11.978
OH, HE'S GOING FIRST CLASS.

00:11.978 --> 00:13.947
I NEED TO MEET WITH YOU TODAY.

00:13.947 --> 00:16.583
GO TALK TO YOUR WIFE. NOW DON'T
CALL MY DAMN PHONE NO MORE.

00:16.583 --> 00:18.519
I GUARANTEE YOU WHEN I FIND
THAT SON OF A BITCH,

00:18.519 --> 00:20.286
I AM GOING TO TEAR
HIS HEART OUT.

00:20.286 --> 00:22.989
THAT CHILD WELFARE LADY WAS
THERE WHEN HE TOOK MY MONEY.

00:22.989 --> 00:24.290
HOW MUCH DID HE PAY?

00:24.290 --> 00:25.626
I DON'T KNOW WHAT
YOU'RE TALKING ABOUT.

00:25.626 --> 00:28.428
[ SCREAMING ]

00:28.428 --> 00:30.430
[ GRUNTING ]

00:31.131 --> 00:34.735
[ SOBBING ]

00:34.735 --> 00:39.405
[ SIGHS ]
YOU MADE ME BREAK MY DAMN NAIL.

00:39.405 --> 00:41.742
WHEW!

00:41.842 --> 00:44.244
[ SOBBING CONTINUES ]

00:51.685 --> 00:53.086
ARE YOU READY TO TALK?

00:55.488 --> 00:57.991
OKAY.

00:57.991 --> 01:00.667
OKAY.

01:03.336 --> 01:06.507
I DON'T KNOW
WHERE HE IS.

01:06.507 --> 01:11.044
I DON'T KNOW.

01:11.044 --> 01:12.679
HOW DID HE PAY YOU?

01:12.679 --> 01:15.949
[ BREATHING SHAKILY ]

01:15.949 --> 01:17.784
ANSWER HER.

01:20.721 --> 01:23.724
IN CASH.

01:23.724 --> 01:26.426
HOW MUCH?

01:26.426 --> 01:27.994
$25,000.

01:27.994 --> 01:32.098
[ SCOFFS ]
$25,000?

01:32.098 --> 01:37.337
WELL, IT SURE AIN'T
IN THIS PURSE.

01:39.840 --> 01:42.008
HOW DID IT WORK?

01:42.008 --> 01:45.912
WHAT?

01:45.912 --> 01:48.615
I WANT TO KNOW
EVERYTHING.

01:49.616 --> 01:52.385
ALL THAT HE SAID

01:52.385 --> 01:57.223
WAS THAT HE'D PAY ME
IF I TOLD YOU

01:57.223 --> 02:00.534
THAT A JUDGE NEEDED TO SEE YOU
HAD A LOT OF MONEY IN THE BANK.

02:00.534 --> 02:02.836
THAT'S IT.

02:02.836 --> 02:05.005
THAT'S ALL I DID.

02:05.005 --> 02:07.974
THAT'S ALL I DID.

02:07.974 --> 02:10.110
WHERE'S THE CASH
THAT HE GAVE YOU?

02:10.110 --> 02:12.579
I SPENT IT.

02:12.579 --> 02:14.247
ALL OF IT?

02:14.247 --> 02:17.283
YES.

02:17.283 --> 02:18.985
WAIT, PLEASE DON'T
TELL ANYBODY.

02:18.985 --> 02:21.221
I COULD LOSE MY JOB.
I WON'T CALL THE POLICE.

02:21.221 --> 02:22.689
JUST PLEASE DON'T
TELL ANYBODY.

02:22.689 --> 02:25.125
POLICE?
[ SCOFFS ]

02:25.125 --> 02:27.460
BITCH, YOU COULD LOSE
YOUR DAMN LIFE RIGHT NOW

02:27.460 --> 02:30.330
IF YOU DON'T GIVE ME
MY $25,000 BACK.

02:33.667 --> 02:35.636
OKAY.

02:35.636 --> 02:37.203
I'LL...

02:37.203 --> 02:41.542
I'LL ‐‐ I'LL GO TO
MY CREDIT UNION.

02:43.276 --> 02:45.779
I WANT $100,000.

02:45.779 --> 02:49.716
[ SIGHS ]
I CAN'T GET $100,000.

02:52.619 --> 02:54.621
YOU'D BETTER.

02:56.389 --> 02:59.726
OKAY. OKAY. I'LL TRY.

02:59.726 --> 03:01.568
YOU GOT SIX HOURS.

03:01.568 --> 03:04.304
SIX HOURS?!
ARE YOU...ARE YOU CRAZY?

03:04.304 --> 03:06.573
I CAN'T GET IT
IN SIX HOURS.

03:06.573 --> 03:08.742
YOU DON'T KNOW
I'M CRAZY BY NOW?

03:11.144 --> 03:12.979
AND MY SON.

03:12.979 --> 03:13.980
YOUR SON?

03:13.980 --> 03:16.583
WAIT.
I ‐‐ I CAN'T DO THAT.

03:17.818 --> 03:20.486
LISTEN TO ME.

03:20.486 --> 03:24.290
I'M SERIOUS.

03:24.290 --> 03:28.662
I'M GOING TO LET YOU
WALK OUT THAT DOOR RIGHT NOW.

03:28.662 --> 03:34.835
YOU HAVE SIX HOURS TO GET ME
MY MONEY AND MY SON.

03:34.835 --> 03:41.742
AND A RECOMMENDATION FROM YOU
THAT I SHOULD HAVE CUSTODY.

03:41.742 --> 03:43.644
DO YOU UNDERSTAND ME?

03:43.644 --> 03:47.147
YES.

03:49.916 --> 03:52.052
I WANT TO KNOW
WHERE OSCAR IS.

03:52.052 --> 03:53.219
I DON'T KNOW.

03:53.219 --> 03:55.021
WELL,
YOU'D BETTER FIND HIM.

03:55.021 --> 03:56.189
HOW?

03:56.189 --> 03:57.357
I DON'T KNOW.

03:57.357 --> 04:00.534
FIND OUT.

04:00.534 --> 04:02.669
I DON'T KNOW.

04:02.669 --> 04:05.171
GET YOUR SORRY ASS
OUT OF HERE.

04:07.407 --> 04:09.943
[ SIGHS ]

04:09.943 --> 04:12.613
[ SNIFFLING ]

04:21.822 --> 04:23.890
YOU KNOW WE MAY NOT
FIND HIM?

04:23.890 --> 04:26.392
WE HAVE TO.

04:26.392 --> 04:28.829
I HOPE YOU'RE THINKING ABOUT
PLAN B.

04:28.829 --> 04:30.831
♪♪♪♪

04:32.933 --> 04:35.969
